{{year-header}}
==January==
* '''[[29 January|29]]''' - [[Richard E. Blackwelder]], Tolkien collector, is born.
==June==
* '''[[10 June|10]]''' - Around this date [[J.R.R. Tolkien]] composes the [[Book of the Foxrook]].
==August==
* '''[[20 August|20]]''' - [[André Morell]], who would play [[Elrond]] in [[The Lord of the Rings (1978 film)|''The Lord of the Rings'' (1978 film)]], is born.
==Autumn==
* [[Francis Xavier Morgan|Father Morgan]] discovers the romance between [[J.R.R. Tolkien]] and [[Edith Tolkien|Edith Bratt]], which he fears may lead to early marriage and ruin Tolkien's career prospects. 
* Tolkien fails to win an [[University of Oxford|Oxford]] scholarship.
==?==
* '''?''' - [[Elaine Griffiths]], friend and pupil of [[J.R.R. Tolkien]], is born.
